Pedro Antonio Ruíz Lalinde
Teacher of Geography and History — IES Ciudad de Haro (La Rioja, Spain)

These materials were originally published on his public website:
http://sauce.pntic.mec.es/~prul0001/index.htm (now closed).

This repository has strictly educational and preservation purposes, with no commercial intent, aiming to keep available valuable didactic resources that were once publicly accessible.

All copyrights of the original work belong to the author or his legitimate heirs.
No ownership or commercial rights are claimed over the original materials.

If the copyright holders wish to have the material modified or removed, they may request it by opening an issue in this repository or contacting the maintainer directly.

